img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.name: img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra_Cr_SNR
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.Description: Signal to noise ratio of creatine
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.note: The maximum amplitude of the creatine peak divided by twice the standard deviation of the noise calculated from subspectrum sum
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.table_label: Quality Control - Automatic - Post-processing - MRS - Osprey Unedited

img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.name: img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra_Cr_FWHM
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.Description: Full width at half maximum of creatine
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.note: The width of the creatine peak at half the maximum amplitude calculated as the average of the FWHM of the data and the FWHM of a lorentzian fit calculated from subspectrum sum
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.table_label: Quality Control - Automatic - Post-processing - MRS - Osprey Unedited

img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.name: img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra_water_FWHM
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.Description: Full width at half maximum of reference water peak
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.note: The width of the water peak at half the maximum amplitude calculated as the average of the FWHM of the data and the FWHM of a lorentzian fit
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.table_label: Quality Control - Automatic - Post-processing - MRS - Osprey Unedited

img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.name: img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra_residual_water_ampl
img_osprey_unedited_qm_processed_spectra.note: The amplitude of the water signal removed by the HSVD filter calculated from subspectrum sum
